# Build-time snapshot of parent repo (regenerated by scripts/snapshot-docs.mjs).
# COMMITTED to git so Vercel deployments work without needing to clone the
# parent repo. Local builds refresh it via the prebuild npm script; on Vercel
# (where only ui/ is uploaded) the script skips regeneration and the
# committed copy is used directly.

